com.hazelcast.client.spi

Interface ClientListenerService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ClientListenerServiceImpl, ClientNonSmartListenerService, ClientSmartListenerService

    public interface ClientListenerService
    Client service to add/remove remote listeners.

    For smart client, it registers local listeners to all nodes in cluster. For dummy client, it registers global listener to one node.
